/**
 * YUI Compressor
 * http://developer.yahoo.com/yui/compressor/
 * Author: Julien Lecomte - http://www.julienlecomte.net/
 * Copyright (c) 2011 Yahoo! Inc. All rights reserved.
 * The copyrights embodied in the content of this file are licensed
